message.content: The image depicts a simple, black-and-white line drawing of a diamond shape. The diamond is outlined with thick, black lines and has a symmetrical design. It consists of a central, larger triangle with two smaller, identical triangles positioned on either side. The overall design is geometric and minimalist, emphasizing the shape and structure of the diamond. This type of illustration is commonly used to represent gemstones, jewelry, or luxury items in various contexts.
